  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à juffed</title>

    <para>
      The <application>JuffEd</application> package is a Qt based editor with
      support for multiple tabs. It is simple et clear, but very powerful.
      Supports language syntax highlighting, auto-indents in accordance with
      file type, code blocks folding, maching braces highlighting with instant
      jumps between them, powerful search et replacing text using regular
      expressions (including multiline ones) with the opportunity to use
      matches \1, \2, &hellip; in substitutions, a terminal emulator, saving
      named sessions et many other features.
    </para>

    &lfs77_checked; &gcc5_checked;

